課程概述 Course Description
       讓學生學會如何有效且清楚地口語表達，如何進行小組討論，讓學生可以實際練習所學的語言技巧 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
Plan and organize a presentationDevelop practical presentation skillsGive a presentation confidently and fluently 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Assessment2Orientation3Unit 1: A person to admire: Describing an admirable person's life history & achievements and why you admire the person.4Unit 1: A person to admire: Describing an admirable person's life history & achievements and why you admire the person.5Unit 2: A great vacation: Describing various travel destination, activities & accommodations.6Unit 2: A great vacation: Describing various travel destination, activities & accommodations.7Unit 3: Young people today: Describing a survey's topic & methods and reporting the results.8Unit 3: Young people today: Describing a survey's topic & methods and reporting the results.9Group Presentation10Movie Project11Unit 4 Let me explain: Providing the context or background for a process and explaining the steps of a process.12Unit 4 Let me explain: Providing the context or background for a process and explaining the steps of a process.13Unit 5 In my opinion: Expressing opinions and supporting opinions with reasons.14Unit 5 In my opinion: Expressing opinions and supporting opinions with reasons.15Unit 6 In the news: Summarizing a news story and describing reactions to a news story.16Unit 6 In the news: Summarizing a news story and describing reactions to a news story.17Final Oral Presentation18Final Oral Presentation 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


