學習規範 Course Policy
1. Attendance
Students missing mre than 1 class may have their final course grade lowered. If you must miss class, please let me know before class, or as soon as possible afterwards.
無故曠課一堂課扣總平均1分，兩堂課扣總平均2分，每人每學期可請2小時事假（不用證明口頭請假即可）

2. Participation & Quizzes
Much of the learning in this course will occur through class discussion and in-class experiences. It is critical that students read assigned material before class, and come prepared with any response activities that have been assigned. Please note there will be NO make-up opportunities for class discussions and quizzes. 
課堂小考及課間討論練習無法在課後進行補考

3. Learning Portfolio  
Please prepare a notebook for your class notes, handouts from the teacher or other important class information. 
請準備課堂筆記本

4. The use of cell phones, smart phones, or other mobile communication devices is prohibited during class unless specified otherwise.
嚴禁上課使用手機玩遊戲或流連FB等社群網站，緊急聯絡請至教室外面接聽。      

